Opportunity:

We are seeking a person to join a team within Commodities Quantitative Research supporting the Precious Metals and the Base Metals trading desks. We expect the joiner to share in a balanced mixture of responsibilities, including model research and development, model documentation, development of pricing and risk management tools, product-specific analysis, discussions with the trading desk, sales and control teams.

Core responsibilities:

Developing and enhancing valuation models;
 Implementing valuation and risk management tools within the Athena platform;
 Explain model behavior to the users, including trading, sales and control teams;
 Working in partnership with the sales and trading teams, carrying out scenario analysis, providing guidance on specific transactions;
 Writing well-formulated documents covering model specification and implementation testing.
